  "lore": "Orchids come from across the Misty Sea and can spend years in a peaceful state, contemplating and planning their next move while crystals grow across their skin. Orchids are largely unaffected by their environment, getting whatever warmth and sustenance they need from their meditations, so it is perfectly natural they would eventually find their way into the inhospitable north. These harsher climates provide them with new, unique perspectives on which to ruminate.\n\nAn Orchid’s contemplative nature also gives them a particular prowess over the elemental energies of the world. Some use these energies to attack their foes with raw power; however, others emit these energies into strands of elemental fabric, weaving them into physical armor and weapons. These are the Infusers, martial warriors who use the natural flow of elements to enhance their already formidable fighting skills.",
